name: Alex Clifford
description: I consider myself to be optimistic, faithful, loyal, kind, tender, understanding and respectful. My friends say that I am a soul of any company. I agree with them because I am very communicative and I can get along with any person. I am very active and energetic and it is a great pleasure for me to try new things, to travel and explore new beautiful places. I am open to adventures and in the deep of my soul I dream about the most wonderful and nice adventure which can only happen to me. I like to sing and to my mind I have a very nice voice. I will like meet a woman with good heart that’s fully ready to face relationship not just for fun.
